[[[description]]]
This class entry flag is set when any property accessor magic methods (`__set`, `__isset`, `__unset`, `__get`) have been implemented on a class (see also the [`IS_OBJ_USE_GUARDS`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/is_obj_use_guards) object flag). This is used to ensure that the corresponding magic methods are used for property access instead of the usual direct access (a hash table lookup in the properties table).

